- Alma Lane.

00:10.227 --> 00:11.968
- I found this
in Rothstein's hate mail.

00:12.012 --> 00:13.491
She's an artist.

00:13.535 --> 00:15.493
- I mean, here were versions
of me in some of his books.

00:15.537 --> 00:17.582
- Who were you?
- I was Susan.

00:17.626 --> 00:19.584
- This book is not

00:19.628 --> 00:22.587
on the school board's
approved reading list.

00:22.631 --> 00:24.807
You and Jimmy Gold
will get along.

00:24.850 --> 00:28.071
- I, uh, picked up the listingon the old Bridgeton Jazz Club.

00:28.115 --> 00:30.073
There's a bunch of shit in
there I want you to pick up.

00:30.117 --> 00:31.944
- I may have some materials.

00:31.988 --> 00:34.208
- There's somebody out there
looking for those books

00:34.251 --> 00:35.948
who will kill to get them!

00:35.992 --> 00:38.777
- What about the manuscripts?
- The kid's got 'em.

00:38.821 --> 00:40.344
- You get pickaxe.

00:42.042 --> 00:43.217
[grunts]

00:43.260 --> 00:45.306
- You and me,
I don't think we sustain.

00:45.349 --> 00:48.091
If I continue to see him,
I might fall in love with him.

00:48.135 --> 00:49.571
- You can't break up
with someone

00:49.614 --> 00:51.355
'cause you're afraid
you might love them.

00:51.399 --> 00:53.444
If you like this man,
go be with him.

00:53.488 --> 00:56.404
- Our window is closing.
We need to grab the mother.

00:56.839 --> 00:59.059
- [muffled screaming]

00:59.407 --> 01:01.800
- Marjorie?
Oh, Jesus.

01:01.844 --> 01:03.237
- Petey, remember me?

01:03.280 --> 01:05.065
And, of course,
you remember your mother.

01:05.108 --> 01:07.241
- [muffled scream]
- Don't you fucking touch her!

01:07.284 --> 01:09.678
- We will be making a plan
for the book delivery

01:09.721 --> 01:12.507
or it's mommy deadest.

01:12.550 --> 01:14.639
[dramatic music]

01:14.683 --> 01:20.167
♪

01:22.865 --> 01:24.258
- Hi, this is Danielle.

01:24.301 --> 01:26.173
Leave a message
after the beep.

01:26.216 --> 01:28.218
- All right, look...
[sighs]

01:28.262 --> 01:33.093
First, it's fucking cruel,
borderline inhumane,

01:33.136 --> 01:35.269
not to at least let me know
you're okay.

01:35.312 --> 01:36.705
Second...

01:37.358 --> 01:40.274
If I get wind that you're with
some other guy, you are dead.

01:40.317 --> 01:42.145
You hear me?
Him, too.

01:42.189 --> 01:44.626
You're both dead.

01:44.669 --> 01:48.151
And third, come on.
[scoffs]

01:48.195 --> 01:50.762
You can't do better
than me, Danielle.

01:50.806 --> 01:53.896
Women, you all say
you want a good guy.

01:53.939 --> 01:56.942
Somebody trustworthy
and dependable and sensitive

01:56.986 --> 02:00.076
and all that crap, which is
total fucking bullshit.

02:00.120 --> 02:03.123
Those are the assholes
who get cheated on or dumped.

02:03.166 --> 02:07.301
You all want the bad boy,
and I am it, baby.

02:07.344 --> 02:09.781
I'm good-looking,
I'm unpredictable,

02:09.825 --> 02:11.131
and I fuck good.

02:11.174 --> 02:13.698
It's the goddamn triple crown!

02:13.742 --> 02:15.178
You will come
crawling back to me!

02:15.222 --> 02:18.225
It's only a matter of time,
you piece of shit.

02:20.227 --> 02:21.489
Fuck.

